Expected to sell soon – Tour it in person or via video chat before it's gone!

Spectacular downtown and city views from this beautiful and spacious midcentury condo in Anza Vista! This rarely available, light and bright condo features an open living/dining area, upgraded kitchen with quartz counters and new appliances, handsome wood floors, generous in-unit closets, deeded parking and additional storage unit. Ideal central city location in a reserved, established neighborhood and in close proximity to Golden Gate Park, Laurel Village, NOPA, USF, JCC, Kaiser, Trader Joes. You'll love the colorful morning sunrises, afternoon 'golden hour' glow of the city skyline, and dazzling fireworks during NYE/4th of July from your own private deck! Fully owner occupied building with HOA reserves and shared garden.
